flowchart TD
    A[Start main.py] --> B[Import run_agent from agent]
    B --> C[Call run_agent()]
    C --> D[Load .env and API key in agent.py]
    D --> E[Import available_functions from functions]
    E --> F[Import tools from schemas]
    F --> G[Initialize messages with system prompt]
    G --> H{User input}
    H -- exit/quit --> I[End]
    H --> J[Append user message to messages]
    J --> K[First API call with tools]
    K --> L{Tool calls present?}
    L -- yes --> M[Append tool call to messages]
    M --> N[For each tool call: Invoke function via map]
    N --> O[Append tool result to messages]
    O --> P[Second API call for final answer]
    P --> Q[Print final answer]
    Q --> H
    L -- no --> R[Print response directly]
    R --> H